Sentencas: Cell performance was measured at 773-1073 K for Ni-GDC(Gd-doped ceria) anode-supported GDC film (60 mu m thickness) with SrRuO3 cathode using a 3 vol% H2O-containing H-2 fuel.
Titulo: Cell performance of strontium ruthenium oxide cathode/Gd-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte/nickel-GDC anode system

Sentencas: Reduction of particle size (< 1 mu m) of SrRuO3 cathode was effective to decrease the voltage drop at the cathode because of the increased length of triple phase boundary (GDC electrolyte-SrRuO3 cathode-O-2 gas).
Titulo: Cell performance of strontium ruthenium oxide cathode/Gd-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte/nickel-GDC anode system

Sentencas: Open circuit voltage (OCV) of GDC electrolyte in an anode atmosphere without H-2 fuel was close to the value calculated by Nernst equation for no electronic conduction.
Titulo: Cell performance of strontium ruthenium oxide cathode/Gd-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte/nickel-GDC anode system

Sentencas: However, the OCV in a H-2-containing atmosphere decreased from the values by Nernst equation owing to the increased electronic conduction in a GDC mull.
Titulo: Cell performance of strontium ruthenium oxide cathode/Gd-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte/nickel-GDC anode system

Sentencas: This tendency of decrease in OCV became significant for thinner GDC film.
Titulo: Cell performance of strontium ruthenium oxide cathode/Gd-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte/nickel-GDC anode system

Sentencas: This result was interpreted by the dissolution and dissociation of H-2 fuel in a GDC film to form protons and electrons (H-2 -> 2H(+) + 2e(-)).
Titulo: Cell performance of strontium ruthenium oxide cathode/Gd-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte/nickel-GDC anode system
